;:&quot;-U&quot;}\" data-lynx-mode=\"asynclazy\" data-lynx-uri=\"https://l.facebook.com/l.php?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FM2c6pJ&amp;h=ATO0Ij7GkwtAu8dzLs77OBHKU4dGomtS8hBB9BhzYsii-7HehDwJRNrJ8GtIqTSQKQo5IqQHy_-CQyjKccsdEKkH7grVCHF3uNqmLTE_ISw3BunHccNZ6M03gWNP9N3eIA-xllrLNRcqKXg\" href=\"https://goo.gl/M2c6pJ\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" style=\"color: rgb(54, 88, 153); cursor: pointer; text-decoration-line: none; font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, system-ui, &quot;.SFNSText-Regular&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/M2c6pJ</a><span style=\"color: rgb(29, 33, 41); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, system-ui, &quot;.SFNSText-Regular&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span><br />\r\n<span class=\"text_exposed_show\" style=\"display: inline; font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, system-ui, &quot;.SFNSText-Regular&quot;, sans-serif; color: rgb(29, 33, 41);\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">----------------------------------------</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Th&ocirc;ng tin chi tiết xin vui l&ograve;ng li&ecirc;n hệ:</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Trung t&acirc;m Cung ứng nguồn nh&acirc;n lực , Học viện N&ocirc;ng nghiệp Việt Nam</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 0px; white-space: nowrap;\">&nbsp;</span></span><span class=\"text_exposed_show\" style=\"display: inline; font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, system-ui, &quot;.SFNSText-Regular&quot;, sans-serif; color: rgb(29, 33, 41); font-size: 14px;\">Hotline: 0981.686.486 - 0977.116.847 - 0984.798.433 - 0912.188.182&nbsp;<br />\r\nFanpage : Trung t&acirc;m Cung ứng nguồn nh&acirc;n lực VNUA - Cổng th&ocirc;ng tin việc l&agrave;m Học viện N&ocirc;ng Nghiệp Việt Nam&nbsp;<br />\r\nEmail: cungungnguonnhanluc@vnua.edu.vn<br />\r\nXin ch&acirc;n th&agrave;nh cảm ơn - 心から、ありがとう !</span></p>\r\n',0,1,'2604/thong-bao-tuyen-thuc-tap-sinh-nganh-dich-vu-lam-viec-tai-nhat-ban-thang-4_1524717473.jpg',NULL,NULL,1,'2018-04-18 10:23:34','