t-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(29, 33, 41);\" />\r\n<span .sfnstext-regular=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(29, 33, 41);\">Email: cungungnguonnhanluc@vnua.edu.vn</span><br .sfnstext-regular=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(29, 33, 41);\" />\r\n<span .sfnstext-regular=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(29, 33, 41);\">Xin ch&acirc;n th&agrave;nh cảm ơn - 心から、ありがとう !</span></p>\r\n',0,1,'0509/phong-van-du-hoc-dai-hoc-quoc-gia-incheon-han-quoc-tai-hoc-vien-nong-nghiep-viet-nam_1536135724.jpg',NULL,NULL,1,'2018-09-05 15:22:04','2018-09-05 15:22:04',1,NULL,NULL,0),
