t; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1); color: rgb(29, 33, 41); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\" />\r\n<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1); color: rgb(29, 33, 41); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">- Tr&igrave;nh độ: tốt nghiệp Đại học đ&uacute;ng chuy&ecirc;n ng&agrave;nh, ưu ti&ecirc;n sinh vi&ecirc;n Học viện N&ocirc;ng nghiệp Việt Nam</span><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);\" />\r\n<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1); color: rgb(29, 33, 41); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">*&nbsp;</span><span class=\"text_exposed_show\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1); display: inline; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(29, 33, 41);\">Phỏng vấn: dự kiến 15/9/2018</span><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);\" />\r\n<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1); color: rgb(29, 33, 41); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">*&nbsp;</span><span class=\"text_exposed_show\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1); display: inline; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(29, 33, 41);\">Dự kiến xuất cảnh: th&aacute;ng 4/2019</span><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);\" />\r\n<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1); color: rgb(29, 33, 41); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">*&nbsp;</span><span class=\"text_exposed_show\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1); display: inline; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(29, 33, 41);\">Địa điểm l&agrave;m việc: Tỉnh Aomori, Nhật Bản</span><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);\" />\r\n<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1); color: rgb(29, 33, 41); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">*&nbsp;</span><span class=\"text_exposed_show\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1); display: inline; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(29, 33, 41);\">Mức lương: 36 - 38 triệu/th&aacute;ng - chưa bao gồm l&agrave;m th&ecirc;m, ng&agrave;y nghỉ theo quy định Nhật Bản</span><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);\" />\r\n<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1); color: rgb(29, 33, 41); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">*&nbsp;</span><span class=\"text_exposed_show\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1); display: inline; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(29, 33, 41);\">Thời gian hợp đồng: 3 năm&nbsp;</span><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);\" />\r\n